    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A NEW TWIST ON NONOGRAM PUZZLE GAMES</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/f040afb229a29bdce765bb5964acd2b1.poster.avif?t=1757621734\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/f040afb229a29bdce765bb5964acd2b1.webm?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/f040afb229a29bdce765bb5964acd2b1.mp4?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> In GRIDHACK, hacking = solving nonograms.<br></li><li> Solve the logic puzzles to attack the firewall.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/94cc1173f1636d583be7cf54bdd496e8.poster.avif?t=1757621734\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/94cc1173f1636d583be7cf54bdd496e8.webm?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/94cc1173f1636d583be7cf54bdd496e8.mp4?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The nonogram battle system adds action, tension and new strategies to traditional puzzle solving.<br></li><li> Use module abilities to defend, attack or manipulate the grid. Experiment with different loadouts to <strong>fit to your play style</strong>.<br></li><li> Stay alive while fighting the firewall. Level up to face tougher challenges.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMBARK ON A SCI-FI ADVENTURE</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/5c555602b6592901a5f495291bc6d1cb.poster.avif?t=1757621734\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/5c555602b6592901a5f495291bc6d1cb.webm?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/5c555602b6592901a5f495291bc6d1cb.mp4?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Embark on an epic sci-fi journey through exotic locations.<br></li><li> Use your hacking skills to take back systems, open locks, reveal secrets.<br></li><li> Try to find answers about what happened to the planet called <i>Earth</i>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/a0bd4aecf48c307bdb93aee428e14d9a.poster.avif?t=1757621734\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/a0bd4aecf48c307bdb93aee428e14d9a.webm?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053870/extras/a0bd4aecf48c307bdb93aee428e14d9a.mp4?t=1757621734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> It's a big galaxy out there. Thankfully, you're not alone: Get to know a rag-tag crew of eclectic characters.<br></li><li> The universe is rarely black and white… <strong>which shade of gray will you land on?</strong></li></ul>",
